Info about the episode:

While on her way to her grandmother&#039;s birthday party, 

Alex&#039;s day gets sidetracked when she tries to save a diamond 

runner, named Ben, whose partners, Lisa and Jason, want to silence

him for good which leads to a standoff in an underwater cave with

Alex and Ben trying to avoid the rising tide and the smugglers 

circling above in their motorboat. Meanwhile, Hobie and Mitch begin

to get on each other&#039;s case over privacy in the house, which 

prompts Hobie to think about moving out. But when Hobie cannot 

get in with his friends, Neely Capshaw returns and gives Hobie 

an lucrative offer to move in with her for a while which makes 

Mitch angry knowing that Neely always has an agenda.
